        {
            "title": "OpenAI未達內部營收及用戶目標——《華爾街日報》報導",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據《<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"華爾街日報\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:華爾街日報;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華爾街日報\">華爾街日報</a>》週一報導,OpenAI近期未能達成其自訂的新用戶和營收目標,引發外界對這家人工智能新創公司如何支撐其龐大支出計劃的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》援引知情人士消息稱,這家新創公司未能達成在2025年底前讓其ChatGPT聊天機器人達到10億週活躍用戶的內部目標。此外,該公司今年稍早也多次未能達成月度營收目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》報導稱,OpenAI首席財務官薩拉·弗里爾(Sarah Friar)向公司其他領導層表示,她擔心如果營收增長不夠快,公司可能無法支付未來的數據中心合約費用。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ad927cf5-fb8d-3817-bdb3-25914ef6d5d7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》報導指出,OpenAI董事會成員也在審查該公司最近的數據中心交易,並質疑執行長薩姆·奧特曼(Sam Altman)在營收疲軟的情況下仍努力爭取更多運算能力的做法。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對OpenAI營收和支出的擔憂正值這家AI新創公司加速推進首次公開募股之際,預計IPO將在今年底前進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》報導稱,首席財務官弗里爾和其他高層現正尋求更嚴格地控制成本,並建立更嚴謹的商業紀律。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI在過去一年進行了大規模的交易,承諾在未來幾年投入約6000億美元建設數據中心。但與此同時,來自Anthropic和Google等競爭對手的競爭也日益激烈,這些公司的先進AI模型被認為在性能上與OpenAI不相上下,甚至有所超越。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/openai%E6%9C%AA%E9%81%94%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E-033104655.html",
